{"tid":1866950,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"網購外科口罩集運討論 3","createTime":"2020-02-07T03:30:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-07T05:42:07.000Z","uid":159697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"da703faeeb76e86753014da20b5c5e5518c4ec95","tid":1866950,"uid":159697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T03:30:55.000Z","msg":"內容及資料僅供參考，投資涉及風險，口罩價格可升亦可跌，甚至變成亳無價值。投資者在決定是否購買有關口罩之前應先閱讀有關風險評估，以了解該建議發售之詳細資料，並應就本身的財務、其他狀況及需要，詳細考慮並決定購買有關口罩是否切合本身特定的需要，若有需要更應咨詢其他專業意見，方可作出有關購買決定。<br />\n忠告：親自買罩 咪俾錢炒狗<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n間間集運都爆，唔好再問邊間快啲邊間好用，根本就無人知。記得留意返集運公司對體積重收費同要求，隨時運費貴過口罩本身，重有拒收嘅風險存在。<br />\n<br />\nAmazon自己送<br />\nKatolec=老人<br />\nYamato=貓<br />\n<br />\n麻煩大家Amazon唔好再用殘體字 有得揀英文/日文<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"219e35fd51484ee5aa057122640d5d87c69ad71c","tid":1866950,"uid":159697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T03:32:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0793458cf06575af0a47fb5fe41e60e7bfd500a5","tid":1866950,"uid":239696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T05:27:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69b3f719ff22941d3b9aa49a0dd8c6f52d55ba05","tid":1866950,"uid":50703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0793458cf06575af0a47fb5fe41e60e7bfd500a5","tid":1866950,"uid":239696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T05:27:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T05:42:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}